question: Will Sam Altman join Grok by Dec 31?
description:
This market will resolve to "Yes" if Sam Altman officially joins xAI/Grok, in any capacity, by December 31, 2023, 11:59 PM ET. Otherwise this market will resolve to "No."

Joining Grok could involve, but is not limited to, becoming an employee, advisor, board member, or taking on an executive role within the company. Confirmation must come from an official xAI/Grok announcement, an official statement by Sam Altman or Elon Musk, or credible news reporting.

question: Was Sam Altman fired due to data leak / privacy issue?
description:
This market will resolve to "Yes" if definitive evidence is released that at least part of the reason Sam Altman was fired as CEO of OpenAI was due to a data leak/privacy issue by November 30, 11:59 PM ET. Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".

The primary resolution source for this market will be official information from OpenAI and/or Sam Altman, however a consensus of credible reporting will also be used.

question: Sam Altman announces new company by Nov 24?
description:
This market will resolve to "Yes" if Sam Altman officially announces the creation of a new company where he holds a significant position (such as founder, co-founder, CEO, etc.) by November 24, 2023, 11:59 PM ET. Otherwise this market will resolve to "No." 

The announcement must be public and verifiable, and can come via a variety of official channels, including but not limited to, Sam Altman's verified social media accounts, press releases, media reports, or official company announcements. For clarity, the announcement must explicitly reference the creation of a new company and not merely imply it. Note that an announcement by the resolution date of a new company suffices - the company need not be created by the resolution date.
